description: The fund will invest at least 80% of its total assets (but typically far more) in component securities (including depositary receipts in respect of such securities) of the underlying index. The underlying index is designed to track the performance of equity securities of large- and mid-capitalization companies based in the countries in the Economic and Monetary Union (the "EMU" or "Eurozone") of the European Union ("EU").
name: Xtrackers Eurozone Equity ETF
